title: 02/25/22 DPS Hour 3 - Doug Gottlieb & Jason Smith Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 02/25/22 DPS Hour 3 - Doug Gottlieb & Jason Smith Guest Hosting
description:
Doug and Jason talk about the situation in L.A. with Lebron, and whether or not he will be considered a villain when he leaves. Former NFL Scout John Middlekauff joins the guys to talk about Aaron Rodgers and the Packers and the other major headlines around the NFL this week. Plus, Doug and Jason talk about Russell Wilson's future in Seattle.
